<HEADLINE>
FT  01 FEB 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
CURRENCY-LINKED shares lost ground after Thursday's gains as the financial
rand stabilised. The all-gold index shed 28 to 1,246 as world prices
continued weaker. The industrial index was off 22 at 4,401 and the all-share
lost 27 to 3,604.
