helped Goodyear cut debt by Dollars 1bn to about Dollars 2.6bn.
Since Mr Gault took the helm at Goodyear last summer, shortly after he
retired as Rubbermaid's chairman, the company has announced several new
tyres for the North American market.
'Our initiatives should lead to the achievement of our goal of tyre unit
growth in excess of the 2 to 3 per cent annual growth expected in the tyre
industry as a whole,' he said.
